{"tid":1146454,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次毒遊瑞士法國德國10日 一問","createTime":"2019-05-09T08:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T12:52:17.000Z","uid":42148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fefa3e966fdcfc4e570ed09b43d0130c54bbb00","tid":1146454,"uid":42148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"嚟緊5月尾出發，想問吓各位去過嘅巴絲我咁樣plan啲時間會唔會太密?<br />\n因為怕第5日行程太密，住個到就唔知住返Zermatt定係Bern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且去到Day7-Day9又好似有好多時間剩咁<br />\n<br />\nDay1<br />\nHK-&gt;Zurich(朝早6點到)-&gt;Interlaken-&gt;Harder Kulm-&gt;Grindelwald (住）<br />\n<br />\nDay2<br />\nGrindelwald-&gt;First-&gt;Bachalpsee-&gt;Grindelwald (住）<br />\n<br />\nDay3<br />\n少女峰-&gt;Grindelwald (住）<br />\n<br />\nDay4<br />\nGrindelwald-&gt;Interlaken Ost (寄行李)-&gt;Blausee-&gt;Interlaken Ost-&gt;Zermatt(住)<br />\n<br />\nDay5<br />\nZermatt-&gt;Sunnegga Paradise-&gt;Stellisee-&gt;Gornergrat觀景台-&gt;行Rotenboden至Riffelberg-&gt;Riffelsee-&gt;Bern(住)<br />\n<br />\nDay6<br />\nBern-&gt;Basel (住)<br />\n<br />\nDay7<br />\nBasel-&gt;法國Colmar-&gt;Riquewihr-&gt;Colmar(住)<br />\n<br />\nDay8<br />\nColmar-&gt;Strasbourg-&gt;德國Frankfurt-&gt;羅騰堡(住)<br />\n<br />\nDay9<br />\n羅騰堡-&gt;紐倫堡(住)<br />\n<br />\nDay10<br />\n紐倫堡-&gt;HK"},{"pid":"e1519463dd52347d81d516be2ff2c92899553926","tid":1146454,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"day 6 好似無乜嘢做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比我 day 5 會住 zermatt  <br />\n<br />\n前兩日唔好天睇唔到馬特洪峰，都有一日走盞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403e1de9a85b4038324c743613361e85da8cf857","tid":1146454,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"個人認為紐倫堡好悶"},{"pid":"98cff037217af808c2644954be122064b5ffb20f","tid":1146454,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:07:1